query:
SELECT
          tx_hash,
          event_index_in_tx,
          id,
          l2_block_number
        FROM
          withdrawals
        WHERE
          id > COALESCE(
            (
              SELECT
                MAX(l2_block_number)
              FROM
                l2_blocks
              WHERE
                commit_l1_block_number IS NOT NULL
            ),
            1
          )
          AND l2_block_number <= (
            SELECT
              MAX(withdrawal_id)
            FROM
              finalization_data
          )
        ORDER BY
          l2_block_number
        LIMIT
          $1
